Description: Perform quality control analysis to validate the identity of samples
    between multiple DNA or RNA samples, and between DNA and RNA. Preprocess VCF files
    into integer SNP arrays. Correlate SNPs, and form groups of suspected related samples. 
    This is useful to identify and resolve mislabled or "swapped" samples in the dataset.
